com.msd.queryengine

Class QueryBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.msd.queryengine.QueryBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    QueryEngineInterface

    public class QueryBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
implements QueryEngineInterface
    The Class QueryBuilder accepts factory components to build the query. Then frames the final query by making use of the data structures updated by the query builder factory components.
